#. type: Plain text
#: website/content/en/releases/13.0R/relnotes.adoc:380
msgid ""
"Prior releases had a complete ms-dos formatted filesystem packaged into "
"boot1.efifat.  Older versions of FreeBSD installed this filesystem image "
